Class Transaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.firestore.UpdateBuilder<Transaction>
      • com.google.cloud.firestore.Transaction

  • public final class Transaction
extends UpdateBuilder<Transaction>
    A Transaction is passed to a Function to provide the methods to read and write data within the transaction context.
    See Also:
    Firestore#runTransaction(Function)
